    <entry>
      <title>Windows常见故障解决</title>
      <link href="/2020/03/17/Windows%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3/"/>
      <url>/2020/03/17/Windows%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="系统问题"><a href="#系统问题" class="headerlink" title="系统问题"></a>系统问题</h2><h3 id="系统软件问题"><a href="#系统软件问题" class="headerlink" title="系统软件问题"></a>系统软件问题</h3><ol><li><p>开始菜单无反应，任务栏假死，且无法联网</p><ul><li><p>解决方案：</p><ul><li><p>Powershell中输入命令：</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Get-AppxPackage</span> | % &#123; <span class="built_in">Add-AppxPackage</span> <span class="literal">-DisableDevelopmentMode</span> <span class="literal">-Register</span> <span class="string">"<span class="variable">$</span>(<span class="variable">$_</span>.InstallLocation)\AppxManifest.xml"</span> <span class="literal">-verbose</span> &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li></ul></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
